{"tid":1348432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]香城Online小技巧","createTime":"2019-07-22T08:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:34:55.000Z","uid":149878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc62e853935dff9b4fdd564ac096e8be363f71c","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"香城online開服咁耐大家一定有啲技巧想同大家分享,但係又得一兩個又好似唔夠開post,所以我開個集中貼係到分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一</span></span><br />\n我發現水樽盾牌得一個綁喺手係完全唔夠<br />\n得一個樽嘅時候只要唔係100%打落個樽,就會打落隻手到好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oco7H0B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOco7H0B.png&h=1f44a6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以水樽盾最少要同時使用兩個/更多<br />\n減小直接打到手嘅情況<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1bARTY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1bARTY.png&h=700826eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第二</span></span><br />\n當有啲你唔想比cam影到嘅時候<br />\n你可以用電筒or雷射筆(未試過,不過應該差唔多)射到佢爆光,咁就會咩都影唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好用手/雜物直接遮住鏡頭<br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三</span></span><br />\n見到依個post有啲野想講<br />\n消防員太太復述消防員先生的一個信息！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347669</a><br />\n佢入面講到打爛break glass係可以call到消防<br />\n不過係警報去到消防之前係會去咗保安公司先<br />\n而保安公司係<span style=\"color: red;\">可以截停警報</span>令消防收唔到<br />\n所以call消防最好方法係打去<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">27232406</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時係得咁多,大家一齊討論點樣爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5eef4ce8f7d62066e4831736bb1436fff957a3","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:12:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"603887fa83350a9218ffde280ca8a9c46b5871d8","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:12:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec254f84e1176a9088627888a7bee37d76170534","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84bb728e9183e54d608b8777f3d8524ec4d3384c","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8755b7e5bc65bf114220558694964701faf91e8","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"原來開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df1de00a051cc8ab3b461a10556feaa537d803c","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:13:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"822ed6bf01e76ad9565e085a3ddf3f46cdc88912","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"456072586e11d6471e201cab6cd2e3ae68a92ad1","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:14:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1893f893d31a65b599e5d2ace4e46a5b2a9dc6a","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:15:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38939c9170f6a46ef7f302b13cee875216f6a4dd","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e56463cd225993b873d69efb97646d29ed9170d7","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5fbfc97333fa2a3cbf4657cfc9a5c00e9f20007","tid":1348432,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:16:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04c3a728b26fd421e0d67b9b0de673a8443e7